OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSir Alex joins football    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbrain injuries campaign    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sir Alex Ferguson has added his name to
OL,6, a campaign for the Scottish government 
OL,7, to reclassify football-related brain   
OL,8, injuries as industrial injuries.       
OL,10,FThe former Manchester United manager   
OL,11,Fjoins names including Gordon Strachan, 
OL,12,FAlex McLeish, Willie Miller and Craig  
OL,13,FLevein who have signed the open letter.
OL,15,FIt comes after a study found           
OL,16,Fex-professionals were three-and-a-half 
OL,17,Ftimes more likely to develop dementia. 
OL,19,FThe 'Injury Time' campaign is being led
OL,20,Fby MSP Michael Marra.                  
